This should do all that (GetDisplayAlias will grab the alias if it has one, and the name otherwise):
[code:uzjkxeiz]msg (&quot;Your Target (&quot; + GetDisplayAlias(player&#46;opponent) + &quot;) is in Room&quot; + GetDisplayAlias(player&#46;opponent&#46;parent))[/code:uzjkxeiz]

